<div class="banner home">
  <div class="header-text">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8">
          <h1 class="big-text">Handpicked Lodges</h1>
          <h4>Your Highland Holiday Home</h4>
          <p>A collection of luxury and unique self catering dog friendly holiday lodges some with hot tubs in and around Aviemore and the Cairngorms</p>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
              <div class="availability-checker">
                <%= simple_form_for :search, url: properties_path, method: :get do |t| %>
                  <%= t.input :start_date, placeholder: "Check-in", label: false, as: :string, input_html: { class: "start-date-picker", require: true } %>
                  <%= t.input :end_date, placeholder: "Check-out", label: false, as: :string, input_html: { class: "end-date-picker" } %>
                  <%= t.submit "CHECK AVAILABILITY", name: nil, class: "btn btn-success", :input_html => { id: 'products_search' } %>
                <% end %>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <% unless mobile_device? %>
    <section id="section05" class="demo">
      <a href="#scroll-content"><span></span></a>
    </section>
  <% end %>
</div>
<section id="scroll-content">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4">
        <%= link_to properties_path do %>
          <div class="link-card">
            <div class="link-card-content">
              <h4>Child friendly homes</h4>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4">
        <%= link_to properties_path do %>
          <div class="link-card">
            <div class="link-card-content">
              <h4>Cottages in the country</h4>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4">
        <%= link_to properties_path do %>
          <div class="link-card">
            <div class="link-card-content">
              <h4>Accommodation in Aviemore</h4>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4">
        <%= link_to properties_path(query: {pet_friendly: "true"}) do %>
          <div class="link-card">
            <div class="link-card-content">
              <h4>Pet friendly</h4>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4">
        <%= link_to properties_path(query: {wood_stove: "true"}) do %>
          <div class="link-card">
            <div class="link-card-content">
              <h4>Lodges with wood burners</h4>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4">
        <%= link_to properties_path(query: {hot_tub: "true", sauna: "true"}) do %>
          <div class="link-card">
            <div class="link-card-content">
              <h4>Lodges with hot tub / sauna</h4>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<div class="grey-wrapper">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12">
        <h2>The Lodges</h2>
        <p>From adventurous family summer holidays in the Cairngorms to luxurious ski accommodation in the winter season, these lodges offer something very special ​all year round.</p>
        <p>All of the lodges are dog friendly and child friendly and have wood-burning stoves. Some offer period features, others are airy and modern. Some are equipped with hot tub, sauna – or both – for a little luxury.</p>
        <p>All our self-catering holiday homes are very different – which will become your favourite? Whether it is a cosy little retreat near the centre of Aviemore, or a large country lodge with views down to the river, we have a holiday home that you are sure to fall in love with. However, don't take our word for this please visit our Reviews Page!</p>
        <%= link_to properties_path do %>
          <div class="btn btn-success" style="margin: 0 0 15px 0px">BOOK NOW</div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
      <h2>Handpicked Lodges</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8">
      <p>Each Handpicked Lodge is unique and full of character. As our guests, you can enjoy them as a warm and welcoming home from home during your Highland holiday.</p>
      <p>We provide you with a uniquely personal service from checking every lodge prior to each guest's arrival, to negotiating great deals for you with other local businesses.</p>
      <p>The Cairngorms National Park is not just where we live it is our passion, and as such we are more than happy to share our knowledge and recommendations with you before or during your stay.</p>
      <p>We hope you have a truly wonderful holiday in our very special part of the world. We look forward to welcoming you to your handpicked lodge!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
      <div class="link-card">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="grey-wrapper">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12">
        <h2>Latest Reviews</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <% @reviews.each do |review| %>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
          <p class="text-center"><em>"<%= review.content %>"</em></p>
          <p class="text-center"><%= review.property.name %></p>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12">
        <%= link_to pages_reviews_path do %>
          <div class="btn btn-success" style="margin: 0 0 15px 0px">REVIEWS</div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
      <h2>Live News</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
      <div class="fb-page" data-height="300" data-href="https://www.facebook.com/HandpickedLodges/" data-tabs="timeline" data-small-header="true" data-adapt-container-width="true" data-hide-cover="false" data-show-facepile="false"><blockquote cite="https://www.facebook.com/HandpickedLodges/" class="fb-xfbml-parse-ignore"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/HandpickedLodges/">HandpickedLodges</a></blockquote></div>
    </div>
    <% @posts.each do |post| %>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
        <%= link_to post_path(post) do %>
          <div class="link-card-cloudinary" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.2)), url('<%= cl_image_path post.photo %>');">
            <div class="link-card-content">
              <h4><%= post.title %></h4>
              <p><%= post.created_at.strftime('%d %b, %Y') %></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
